        <h2>Usage</h2>
        <div class="guidelinesColumns">
            <div fxFlex="360px">
                <p>A grid list is best suited to presenting homogenous data, typically images, and is optimized for visual comprehension
                    and differentiating between similar data types.</p>
            </div>

