        <h2>Content</h2>
        <div class="guidelinesColumns">
            <div fxFlex="360px">
                <h3>Content in tiles</h3>
                <p>Tile content consists of primary content and secondary content. Primary content is the main differentiating
                    element, typically an image. Secondary content can be an action or text.</p>
                <br />
                <p>Provide a default image for tiles that lack an image for primary content.</p>
            </div>

            <div fxFlex="360px">
                <img src="assets/images/gridlist/components_grids_content1.png" width="360" /><br />
